# Docker build context exclusions
# Mirrors .gitignore + agent worktree dirs that are not part of the production build.
# Without this, build context balloons to 950MB+ (verified 2026-05-02 — 32 leftover
# *.exe test binaries totaling 793MB plus .claude/worktrees/, hit depot deadline).

# Git
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# Agent / IDE
.claude
.research
.idea
.vscode
.cursor
*.swp

# Build artifacts (Go)
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
*.bin
*.test
*.prof
*.cov
*.out
coverage.out
coverage.html
kite-mcp-server
main

# Test fixtures + ad-hoc scratch HTML
app_*.html
ch.html
*.tmp
*.temp
*.log

# Environment / secrets — never copy into image
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Docs / dev-only — image doesn't need them
docs
.github
tests/e2e
plan
node_modules

# Backup artifacts
*.bak
*.backup
go.sum.backup

# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Keep these (NEEDED for runtime, do not exclude):
#  LICENSE, NOTICE — copied at line 20-21 of Dockerfile
#  etc/litestream.yml — copied at line 23
#  scripts/run.sh — copied at line 24
#  kc/templates/*.html — embedded for landing/dashboard rendering at runtime
